Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ren'ichi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.33,0:00:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you keep the fact that we went to the pool\Nyesterday a secret from Nanase-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.96,0:00:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.30,0:00:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanae...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.97,0:00:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Amagi-kun? Hey, Amagi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.85,0:00:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.06,0:00:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanae's in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.65,0:00:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But she can be a bit insecure and shy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.62,0:00:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,so if you don’t be clear with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.75,0:01:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanae...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.97,0:01:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Translation: Voldemort | Edit: Collectr | Timing: MrMew |TS & Encode: ShocWave | QC: Ayanami-\NPresented by Erobeat | http://www.erobeat.net | #erobeat @ irc.rizon.net
