Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.20,0:01:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&HEC7334&\fs24\fscx138\fscy107\pos(375,533)}Episode 2:     . . .  Because Love Has No Logic
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Rinko-chan, your mom seems very strict.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.15,0:01:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez. Rinko-chan, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How was your date today?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.03,0:01:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I just received a call from your teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears you cut class!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like seconds?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, I was just getting to the good part.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Rinko-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.21,0:01:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't need to hang out with\Nthis jerk if you don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Misawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.27,0:02:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Misawa-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.98,0:02:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,When did I drift off? Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis, can I go home-soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Se-n-pa-i.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.49,0:02:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This feels pretty nice, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.87,0:02:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sitting across from each other\Nlike this and talking every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think it's that nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.75,0:02:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.46,0:02:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy I joined the club!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You do look happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.30,0:02:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of nice things have happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I got to be friends with Kanami-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and I also got to meet Shiina-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.93,0:02:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanami? You mean the ko-gal?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though she's in the same class as me,\Nwe've never talked. I was scared of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.40,0:02:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess she's just kind of\Nintimidating. Hard to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She is a lot different from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.99,0:02:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I always thought there was\Nsomething different about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The way she looks, the way she\Ndresses the way she thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But her outward appearance and dress\Nis the same as yours, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.34,0:03:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But you see, when I finally talked to her,\Nwe actually had a great time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought today we’d visit a place\Nthat Kanami really likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.77,0:03:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That Kanami likes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, it probably doesn't serve food.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.06,0:03:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai, you mustn't judge\Non outward appearances.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.53,0:03:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,"Oh dear, I burned the gratin!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Were you trying to imitate me just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't mean to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.79,0:03:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So when I messed up dinner last\Nnight, you weren't stalking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, well, I just thought that it would be funny\Nif Kanami said something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai, it was just your imagination then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it was. You don't really think\NI'd stalk you at your house, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanae.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ren'ichi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nice fragrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.81,0:04:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You can judge a good tea by its fragrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty knowledgeable, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We drink lots of different kinds of tea at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:04:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.74,0:05:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're avoiding me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We went to the pool on Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't hide that from Nanase-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought I'd tell her about it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I tell her, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Don't do that, Ren'ichi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be the one to tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I'm a little scared,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,so please hold me tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And if....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,we can see love in our future,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:06:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,then let's smile more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&HCDDBDF&}Bye, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You re leaving already
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.55,0:06:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&HCDDBDF&}You are my angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I thought I'd go home with Shiina today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,With Shiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.31,0:06:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she's an old friend of Sanae.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it makes me jealous, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I had some friends when I was small,\Nbut I don't see them anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it might make a person jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unusual to stay friends for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I envy Sanae and Shiina\Nfor staying friends for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I get to hang out with her and talk now too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! That's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.93,0:06:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,se-c-r-et!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a secret between girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it just me, or does that sound kinda nasty?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What? That’s not it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you being nasty, Senpai, for thinking that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I thought so. You're a beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.54,0:07:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! I'm not a beast. Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.42,0:07:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a joke! A joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, Senpai, see you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotaro doesn't have enough experience,\Nso I thought I'd take him out for some.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I never said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.61,0:07:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just jumping to conclusions, Takeaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But you shouldn't say things like that either!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.95,0:07:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll embarrass yourself in front of Misawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.12,0:07:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need to worry about that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you! Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm uncomfortable that you're taking\Nhim to such a seedy place for "experience".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're both still in high school, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to be so rude about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Ren'ichi-kun, try to talk him out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeaki-san, Mizuho-san says\Nshe hates that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably should stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.10,0:08:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making me look like the bad guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.23,0:08:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If Mizuho-san weren't here, you would've\Njumped at the opportunity to come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging by your past behavior...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not what I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think I'd "jump at the\Nopportunity" to go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&HCEE0E5&}Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.70,0:08:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop even considering whether you're going there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You can say that all you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's our own choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And we have our reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, just drop it for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really like this, but whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I won't go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:09:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But, if I could, I'd want to be even\Nbetter friends with you, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.57,0:09:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And that... I guess is just me being selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Nanase, did Sanae tell you anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.41,0:09:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanae-senpai, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.33,0:09:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really. She hasn't told me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it sort of a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanase, listen, what kinds of things do\Nyou usually talk about with Sanae?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Good question. Usually we talk about cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.43,0:09:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She knows a lot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.85,0:09:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.18,0:09:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really understand tennis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And we talk about our problems a lot too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Problems? You mean like studying and college?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.82,0:09:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We do talk about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.74,0:09:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but lately it's been about you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:10:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,However, she's been acting weird a lot lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanae?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she's just not interested in romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, whenever I start talking about it.\Nshe suddenly seems disinterested.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.22,0:10:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather than not being interested in romance...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,she's not interested in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Not interested in me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say something to her\Nrecently that might've upset her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah-ha! You just thought of\Nsomething, didn't you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.41,0:10:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really. Nothing comes to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Something still doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.25,0:10:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah-ha! Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,that Sanae-senpai is in love with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be true, can it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she's known that I loved you\Neven before she even joined the club!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I still haven't told her anything.
